    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong data-start=\"397\" data-end=\"442\">Mercy Without End (Reaction; 1/Long Rest)</strong><br data-start=\"442\" data-end=\"445\" />You refuse to surrender compassion, even at great cost.</p><p data-start=\"502\" data-end=\"661\">When an ally you can see within <strong data-start=\"534\" data-end=\"545\">30 feet</strong> would be reduced to <strong data-start=\"566\" data-end=\"582\">0 hit points</strong>, you may use your <strong data-start=\"601\" data-end=\"613\">reaction</strong> to instead reduce that ally to <strong data-start=\"645\" data-end=\"660\">1 hit point</strong>.</p><p data-start=\"663\" data-end=\"682\"><strong data-start=\"663\" data-end=\"682\">When you do so:</strong></p><ul data-start=\"683\" data-end=\"777\"><li data-start=\"683\" data-end=\"732\"><p data-start=\"685\" data-end=\"732\">You immediately gain <strong data-start=\"706\" data-end=\"732\">2 levels of exhaustion</strong></p></li><li data-start=\"733\" data-end=\"777\"><p data-start=\"735\" data-end=\"777\">Your <strong data-start=\"740\" data-end=\"753\">Rage ends</strong> immediately (if active)</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"779\" data-end=\"867\"><strong data-start=\"779\" data-end=\"809\">Once you use this feature,</strong> you cannot use it again until you finish a <strong data-start=\"853\" data-end=\"866\">long rest</strong>.</p><p data-start=\"869\" data-end=\"928\"><br /><code data-start=\"890\" data-end=\"928\">[GAROU_FEATURE] id=mercy-without-end</code></p>",
